DOC.brief_summary: Approximately 140 male female healthy subject randomize ( 1:1 ratio ) receive 120 mg single dose denosumab either 1.7 mL single injection 70 mg/mL denosumab CP4 ( Treatment A ) 1.7 mL single injection 70 mg/mL denosumab CP2 ( Treatment B ) . Subjects admit research facility day -1 remain research facility day 2 . The subject return research facility outpatient basis . The PK , PD , safety assessment conduct inpatient stay regular interval 18-week treatment period .
